{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200641078923264130725.jpeg/FbHuUV916o7R36xF_-dmn9QHM2P6TTk3pLiYv4G4mL8\" alt=\"涉事貨車的倒後鏡留下一縷懷疑屬於事主的頭髮。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>涉事貨車的倒後鏡留下一縷懷疑屬於事主的頭髮。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><p>現場消息指，5.5噸貨車沿茶果嶺道往鯉魚門方向行駛，至一個右彎撞到由左至右過馬路的女途人。女傷者飛彈10多米外，重傷昏迷倒地。該處沒有燈號等設施，死者被撞位置外約30米有行人過路處。</p><p>事件中涉事貨車的左邊車頭擋風玻璃碎裂，倒後鏡留下一縷懷疑屬於事主的頭髮，車頭燈同樣損毀，有零件飛脫；地上遺下一副疑屬於事主的眼鏡。</p><p>據了解，死者持雙程証來港。</p><p>警方經調查後拘捕該名36歲姓林男司機，案件交由東九龍總區交通交通部特別調查隊第一隊跟進。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200498678108160017293.jpeg/2JXw0CS_YqksQu6gmlr0Ly58B9U3yfcRSnagcm92oHI\" alt=\"涉事貨車司機在場協助調查。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>涉事貨車司機在場協助調查。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200291945058304290768.jpeg/RDorJjE4s1zBvLY0Xuuj3eXx-0HppKwOXmEArnthAK4\" alt=\"貨車撞到一名女子。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>貨車撞到一名女子。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200295355158528915837.jpeg/xMzq89TqbUVhyWn8eoa0CLTlQVAj9-9D8tkhAtfZIQI\" alt=\"貨車撞到一名女子。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>貨車撞到一名女子。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200298408742912913856.jpeg/pbpQyNHytJ2lhTxGufiRw_x4wQjwqSHESvqxf2_6sX8\" alt=\"貨車撞到一名女子。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>貨車撞到一名女子。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200301403607040784603.jpeg/-gd6dAanSGwV0j_oud439OzLS0jhLDZJDQa-CygGvgs\" alt=\"貨車零件飛脫。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>貨車零件飛脫。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200304339750912246581.jpeg/MoWc7EScxO1RWig3JICZxe2pY0S5_UPwEgvJmTcLyZk\" alt=\"懷疑屬於事主的眼鏡遺下地上。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>懷疑屬於事主的眼鏡遺下地上。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200290531577856238471.jpeg/tKRjBvGhYH8dSWQSFmeP2FGuFsuquYbmDBQHdCkUB3Q\" alt=\"現場是茶果嶺道近油塘站對開。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>現場是茶果嶺道近油塘站對開。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200296487751680729184.jpeg/T_pLNSsS-B9t7uJQGEXn8RQOD1d90lm6OG_IVB1vyFQ\" alt=\"涉事貨車的右邊車頭擋風玻璃碎裂，車頭燈亦有損毀。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>涉事貨車的右邊車頭擋風玻璃碎裂，車頭燈亦有損毀。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123200301932220416764123.jpeg/mVgZSp2n8M0R-JrVf7Darxdkw9OMf4hQipWwja-VsI0\" alt=\"警員在場調查。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>警員在場調查。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251008/1052401535708827648547283.jpeg/30CVX962VYGPKDJybvU_DapfIEUT8Z53ugEM4roBDOI\" alt=\"基督教聯合醫院。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>基督教聯合醫院。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T09:20:11.609434+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":429,"images":11,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}